Welcome to Leckner Ford 













Â Â Â Save up to $100 per month on your car payment, only at Leckner Ford.Â Leckner is one of the fastest growing automotive dealer groups in the United States. Our expert automotive staff in our dealerships serve our local communities with quality new and pre-owned vehicles, service and parts. Leckner pricing is so outstanding that people from across the nation choose to buy their vehicles from us. We excel in customer service, and we exceed customer expectations from their initial purchase to the ongoing maintenance of their vehicles. At Leckner, we are proud to serve our customers to meet all of their automotive needs.Leckner Ford has huge savings on every model! You will find the New Ford or Used Ford you are looking for in stock. Find more savings on pre-owned Nissans, Fords, Hondas, Dodges, Chevys and Toyotas; sedans, trucks, SUVs, and vans.Â Â Â Leckner Ford knows that you have high expectations. As a Ford dealership we enjoy the challenge of exceeding your needs each and every time. Leckner Ford loves to help its customers by saving them up to $100 per month on their car payment. Â Leckner Ford stocks a wide selection of new and used cars, trucks and SUVs on its King George Virginia lot. We proudly serve the Northern Virginia and Southern Maryland along with communities in King George, Stafford, Fredericksburg, Tappahnnock, Bowling Green, Dahlgren, and Colonial Beach.Â Let one of our factory trained product specialist take the time to explore the features that are important to you and find the New Ford or used car that fits your budget.Â Nothing beats the open road and a we'll take you on a test drive and highlights the features that meet your driving style.Â When you are in the market a new or used vehicle Leckner Ford has the model in stocking Fiesta, Focus, Fusion, C-MAX, Edge, Flex, Fusion Hybrid, Mustang,Â Taurus, Escape, Explorer, Expedition and the complete line up of F-150 and Super-duty trucks. Â In addition, we carry commercial vans and trucksÂ such as the Transit Connect, Transit-150 and Transit-250 for commercial contractors, farmers, towing of horse trailers and fuel efficient delivery vehicles.Be sure to take a look at our sales and service specials for the most up to date offers.Â Our dealership believes that the sale is only the beginning of a long term relation. Let our factory trained service advisers, certified parts associates and master technicians keep your vehicles in top running condition for years to come. People from King George, Stafford, Fredericksburg, Tappahnnock, Bowling Green, Dahlgren, and Colonial Beach come to Leckner Ford Service Center for all their repair, warranty and maintenance needs.Our Finance Managers understand the bumps in the road of life and will work with you to get you financing. Â We work with the manufacturer's credit company and many other banks and credit unions to get you in to a new or used vehicle. We will take the time to explain the terms, options and benefits of extended warranties we offer.Please let our team know how we can serve all your transportation needs.Â Visit us at: 16057 James Madison Parkway in King George, VA Â 22485 or call (540) 709-1280 for immediate assistance.Â Â Â 
















