Leckner Ford Two, LLC $3,000,000 Financing | Newest SEC Filings

















Newest Filings











Leckner Ford Two, LLC $3,000,000 Financing
Leckner Ford Two, LLC just submitted form D announcing $3,000,000 equity financing.  This is a new filing. Leckner Ford Two, LLC was able to sell $3,000,000. That is 100% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $3,000,000. The financing was made by 35 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $30,000. The financing document was filed on 2016-10-05. Leckner Ford Two, LLC is based in  430 HOOVER ROAD  WOODSTOCK 22664. The firm's business is Retailing. The firm's revenue range is No Revenues. The form was signed by  Carl Leckner.





SEC FORM D


The Securities and Exchange Commission has not necessarily reviewed the information in this filing and has not determined if it is accurate and complete.The reader should not assume that the information is accurate and complete.



